Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不能打开试卷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了拜托了拜托了拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艰苦的考试也只剩下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试一结束就将迎来盼望已久的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  这东西真的很厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才250日圆好便宜  实在是太便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:28.37,biaoti6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}桂糖甜甜圈·幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你这么转就能转出好成绩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁会拼命读书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说可不对哦  小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这支铅笔可是用灵山富士山上的稀有树木做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的人跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Made in China
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你倒是早点注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中国  也有富士山…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不能光靠瞎蒙或是求神拜佛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不踏踏实实努力一下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看来是要熬通宵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这情况该怎么形容你知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽人事  听天命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦你会尽人事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末考试其实也不算什么  在暑假前的这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的准备工作正在有条不紊地进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密手册？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美的点子引起了大家的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  这个网页就是小芽的力作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是这个样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把数据输入这张表格马上就能反映在网页上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就能实时阅览到学园祭的运行情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时也就这样了  要是有什么意见尽管跟我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}San Diego{\r}\N圣迭戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　Gorilla{\r}\NGo  大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喇  喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Pants{\r}\N内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网页不断地被加以改良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人名义也能参展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,册子上写着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但该做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上什么都行  只要在预算范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校方面进行审查的3天内可以随意尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随意尝试？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我已经先提交了申请书啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暑假结束后还有一次最终确认日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要参展  你可以做最终选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也来申请看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备的50本小册子  很快就分发完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后不得不慌慌张张地连夜赶做新的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来进行的比较顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会的同学们都很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我话先说在这里哦  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险的计划或者是不符合学生本分的申请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不会批准的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有过歌剧乐团的前车之鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭可是长期以来一直延续至今的传统大会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没有说让它正式中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做与不做之间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能很大程度地影响着学园祭的预算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…不过…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生们都十分罕见地积极…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着那番景象…呃…怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人兴奋？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就尽量朝积极的方面去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要点击这些相连且一样的图案…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能超过一定的分数就能得到点数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过使用这些点数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能在学园祭网站上  购买一些特别的虚拟形象之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  那些具体创意的构思就交给你们了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:51.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们最终是要  让大家都能在自己的PDA上进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（PDA=Personal Digital Assistant  就是学美她们腰上带着的那个…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在向外界公开之前要进行充分的试玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好Q～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个  明天的考试没问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通宵奋战考试吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…好热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽  你很怕热？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  感觉是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:28.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（垒球县大会）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑  要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的时候  买冰糕吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边卖的冰糕  我都还没中过奖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（垒球县大会）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热的话在屋里吃冰糕不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在热天底下吃冰糕  才能体会到夏季的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个秘密期待礼卷究竟是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集起来就会有好事情发生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是学美嘛  好像她也没有考虑什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小睦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  垒球部的县大赛最后怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也尽人事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜败乃兵家常事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（未中奖）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我早些注意到就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（圣樱学园垒球部  县大赛  决定最终胜负的惨痛失误）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:41.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得对于新生来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对社团招新然后一拥而上似乎是一种惯例呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中的时候大家都是怎么叫你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那我也可以叫你蜜柑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也叫我小睦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我  上原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么叫我的话  我是不会还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在樱花飞舞时相遇的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有被雨声所抹去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…考前复习？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…无论什么时候看起来都是这么厉害呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我马上把他们赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光香  最近过得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不准直接叫名字  不然我杀了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  睦月你稍微注意一下脚边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收拾一下不就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又不是我放在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁放的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  别把果汁打翻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸巾  拿纸巾来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你开什么电视啊  我要开始复习了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你复习你的有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  光香  这里会变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说了不要直接叫名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  借给你玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的  你们在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了  不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们倒是听我说话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说在客人的面前你们就不觉得丢脸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丢脸的是姐姐你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我要小便…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我忍着！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没事的  我没在意啦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想这么热闹就不会觉得寂寞了  我觉得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于明天考试的范围…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是考试的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个  给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你教教她了  光香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么教不教的  蜜柑你的智能水平和我差不多吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来比一比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们休息一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我们真是勇者啊  是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在期末考试前一天晚上\N甩着手来吃甜甜圈喝牛奶咖啡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者勇者～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  关于学园祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不要说学园祭的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦  那我们聊聊棒球吧  棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要说棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…就聊格斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么职业摔跤怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和格斗是一样的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则太复杂了  我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的兴趣都不一致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会成为朋友呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了怎么了？  也不开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变成一个人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着劝还在的几个人加入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得学生会很不错的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就这样算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再去劝劝看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会弄湿的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能打开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了拜托了拜托了拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一门考试也完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假前的学生会业务就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是结束了也不能太放松了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假期间每周集合一次  进行定期的学园祭准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我提议召开慰劳会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是听我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是来自下岛的特别募捐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好耀眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且车站前的Miss Donut牛奶咖啡可以无限续杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆我们去那里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Donut稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我  非常快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七话  『夏天的结束(byebye)』
